{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/dormant-assets-commission/about","content_id":"47d14c04-9ccd-4b8a-ae80-ca87ea252057","description":"The independent Dormant Assets Commission was formed in March 2016. The work of the Commission has now ended. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Dormant Assets Commission was tasked with identifying new pools of dormant assets and working with industry to encourage the contribution of these assets to good causes. The Commission <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/2-billion-boost-set-to-transform-charity-and-voluntary-sector-funding\">published its report on 3 March 2017</a>. Please click <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dormant-assets-commission-final-report-to-government\">here</a> for a copy of the report.</p>\n\n<p>Should you have questions, please contact <a href=\"mailto:dormant-assets@culture.gov.uk\">dormant-assets@culture.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"The work of the Commission has now ended. ","public_timestamp":"2017-03-06T12:57:24Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2016-03-10T11:48:42Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"organisation":"ec2d53a1-0d51-4c9c-8d14-31cfee762922","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2016-03-09T23:42:59+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/dormant-assets-commission/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/dormant-assets-commission/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/dormant-assets-commission/about","content_id":"47d14c04-9ccd-4b8a-ae80-ca87ea252057","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-03-06T12:57:24Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/dormant-assets-commission/about","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"anal